cards

Class CardStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • cards.CardStack

  • public class CardStack
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the whole Card Stack with 52 cards in it. The Stack holds one instance of each card.
    Author:
    Stefan Fuchs, Jan-Niklas Wortmann
    See Also:
    Collection, Stack
